A Kenyan husband sealed his wife's punani with glue after she cheated on him with four men. BISHOP POKED MY WIFE! Daily Star reported Dennis Mumo from Kitui in southern Kenya confessed his crime to the police, claiming he did it to save his marriage after learning of his wife's affairs. The 36-year-old claimed he learned of the affairs through her social media messages. MAKHI DEMANDS SEX! According to reports, on his last business trip to Rwanda, Mumo sealed his wife's punani with superglue, leaving her in terrible pain and in urgent need for medical attention. Mumo will appear before the Kutui court, where he is expected to be charged with domestic abuse. 